		<b>Comment By Basement flooding, 8-19-11</b>
		<p>Research shows that almost 100% of all basements will suffer some form of basement flooding at some point in their existence.  “Almost 100%” translates into “it’s certain”.  It makes sense, too, because basements are the single lowest location in any structure, and excess water is always going to flow downhill.  Put the two together and you have an unwelcome flooded basement.</p>
		
